    lockPref("urlclassifier.trackingTable", "test-track-simple,base-track-digest256");

    :4: レベル2（厳格）ブロックで固定

    *.cfg / *.jsc:
    lockPref("urlclassifier.trackingTable", "test-track-simple,base-track-digest256,content-track-digest256");

